verifyModule(address).notice: Called by Polymath to verify Module Factories for SecurityTokens to use.A module can not be used by an ST unless first approved/verified by Polymath(The only exception to this is that the author of the module is the owner of the ST)-> Only if Polymath enabled the feature.
